    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Dami and Secret Library”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a mystical storybook world as <strong>Dami</strong>, a young girl on a journey to reunite with her late mother hidden beyond the doors of a magical secret library.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>third-person 3D healing adventure</strong> featuring emotional storytelling, color-based puzzle mechanics, and cinematic cutscenes (illustration &amp; real-time 3D).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>Color Absorb Puzzle System</strong><br>Absorb the power of stars and release their colors onto magical platforms to create bridges, activate mechanisms, and reveal hidden paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/73303ca56d3b71b080c32330a7969535.poster.avif?t=1762361304\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/73303ca56d3b71b080c32330a7969535.webm?t=1762361304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/73303ca56d3b71b080c32330a7969535.mp4?t=1762361304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 <strong>Emotional Story &amp; Cinematic Cutscenes</strong><br>Experience beautifully illustrated scenes and fully 3D real-time cutscenes that bring Dami’s journey to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/10c01bf3c2015eaac987a4d530d7a092.poster.avif?t=1762361304\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/10c01bf3c2015eaac987a4d530d7a092.webm?t=1762361304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/10c01bf3c2015eaac987a4d530d7a092.mp4?t=1762361304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 14<strong> Levels of Exploration</strong> <br>Enjoy over 14<strong> handcrafted stages</strong> filled with puzzles, platforming, and story moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/47d22baa4d3f279000a4cfa181f1a97a.poster.avif?t=1762361304\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/47d22baa4d3f279000a4cfa181f1a97a.webm?t=1762361304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233870/extras/47d22baa4d3f279000a4cfa181f1a97a.mp4?t=1762361304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕒 <strong>Average Playtime: Around 1 Hour</strong><br>Designed for a relaxing and focused experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾 <strong>Save &amp; Load System Included</strong><br>Continue your journey at your own pace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About the Journey</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dami enters the Secret Library—a place where time flows differently and memories come alive.<br>Guided by mysterious lights and ancient music, she begins a heartfelt journey to discover the truth about her mother and herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lose yourself in a fairytale world full of color, mystery, and gentle adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to open the doors of the Secret Library?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Watch the trailer on the store page to see the world of Dami come to life!</strong><br><strong>Have a healing and magical adventure! ✨</strong></p>",
